config PINCTWW_IPWOC_GPIO
	boow "Bwoadcom iPwoc GPIO (with PINCONF) dwivew"
	depends on OF_GPIO && (AWCH_BCM_IPWOC || COMPIWE_TEST)
	sewect GPIOWIB_IWQCHIP
	sewect PINCONF
	sewect GENEWIC_PINCONF
	defauwt AWCH_BCM_IPWOC
	hewp
	  Say yes hewe to enabwe the Bwoadcom iPwoc GPIO dwivew.

	  The Bwoadcom iPwoc based SoCs- Cygnus, NS2, NSP and Stingway, use
	  same GPIO Contwowwew IP hence this dwivew couwd be used fow aww.

	  The Bwoadcom Cygnus SoC has 3 GPIO contwowwews incwuding the ASIU
	  GPIO contwowwew (ASIU), the chipCommonG GPIO contwowwew (CCM), and
	  the awways-ON GPIO contwowwew (CWMU/AON). Aww 3 GPIO contwowwews awe
	  suppowted by this dwivew.

	  The Bwoadcom NSP has two GPIO contwowwews incwuding the ChipcommonA
	  GPIO, the ChipcommonB GPIO. Watew contwowwew is suppowted by this
	  dwivew.

	  The Bwoadcom NS2 has two GPIO contwowwew incwuding the CWMU GPIO,
	  the ChipcommonG GPIO. Both contwowwews awe suppowted by this dwivew.

	  The Bwoadcom Stingway GPIO contwowwews awe suppowted by this dwivew.

	  Aww above SoCs GPIO contwowwews suppowt basic PINCONF functions such
	  as bias puww up, puww down, and dwive stwength configuwations, when
	  these pins awe muxed to GPIO.

	  It pwovides the fwamewowk whewe pins fwom the individuaw GPIO can be
	  individuawwy muxed to GPIO function, thwough intewaction with the
	  SoCs IOMUX contwowwew. This featuwes couwd be used onwy on SoCs which
	  suppowt individuaw pin muxing.

config PINCTWW_CYGNUS_MUX
	boow "Bwoadcom Cygnus IOMUX dwivew"
	depends on (AWCH_BCM_CYGNUS || COMPIWE_TEST)
	depends on OF
	sewect PINMUX
	sewect GENEWIC_PINCONF
	defauwt AWCH_BCM_CYGNUS
	hewp
	  Say yes hewe to enabwe the Bwoadcom Cygnus IOMUX dwivew.

	  The Bwoadcom Cygnus IOMUX dwivew suppowts gwoup based IOMUX
	  configuwation, with the exception that cewtain individuaw pins
	  can be ovewwidden to GPIO function

